node.text:
From the Jeep Wrangler 4xe today to concept vehicles and features in development, welcome to the Jeep Life Electrified. This is the start of the next chapter of the journey we’ve been on together for the last 80 years. Jeep. There’s Only One.

#Jeep #ItsAJeepThing #JeepFamily #JeepLife #JeepLove #JeepWrangler #Wrangler4xe #4xe #PHEV #Freedom #Authentic #Adventure #OIIIIIIIO

node.text:
#MakeADifferenceDay reminds us of how proud we are to be partnered with athletes like @wsl surfer @maliamanuel. When the North Shore flooded in Kauai in 2018, she helped her community by providing food, supplies and support. Comment below and tell us how you plan to make a wave in your community. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

Every summer, the world’s best surfers come to Huntington Beach, California for the U.S. Open of Surfing.
